          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The \"Mahila Swayamsiddha Yojana\" implemented by the Social Justice and Empowerment Department, Government of Rajasthan, aims to provide skill training and self-employment opportunities to widowed, abandoned, and destitute women. Under this scheme, free vocational training is offered in Nariniketan buildings, operated via voluntary organizations."
